  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short horror game where you dig through the flesh of a giant whale to find out what happened to your team.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig a path inside the flesh of a whale</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover strange objects only visible under xray </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >explode the insides of a whale with dynamite</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building dread and paranoia</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short experience meant to be finished in under an hour</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460910/extras/bfaa01a2f7a0603e8ce05d5e43bf2483.poster.avif?t=1772327595\" width=512 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460910/extras/bfaa01a2f7a0603e8ce05d5e43bf2483.webm?t=1772327595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460910/extras/bfaa01a2f7a0603e8ce05d5e43bf2483.mp4?t=1772327595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A giant _____ of indescribable size has washed ashore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Earth has rejected the idea of an unknown biomass this large ever living undiscovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distrust grew all around the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Groups of researchers were sent inside in drills to investigate the creature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After connection to the researchers was cut due to classified reasons, chaos erupted all around the globe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You were sent as a last hope to find truth about the nature of the whale and hopefully lead the lost researchers back to the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short horror game where you dig through the flesh of a giant whale to find out what happened to your team.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig a path inside the flesh of a whale</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover strange objects only visible under xray </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >explode the insides of a whale with dynamite</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building dread and paranoia</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short experience meant to be finished in under an hour</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460910/extras/bfaa01a2f7a0603e8ce05d5e43bf2483.poster.avif?t=1772327595\" width=512 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460910/extras/bfaa01a2f7a0603e8ce05d5e43bf2483.webm?t=1772327595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460910/extras/bfaa01a2f7a0603e8ce05d5e43bf2483.mp4?t=1772327595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A giant _____ of indescribable size has washed ashore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Earth has rejected the idea of an unknown biomass this large ever living undiscovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distrust grew all around the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Groups of researchers were sent inside in drills to investigate the creature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After connection to the researchers was cut due to classified reasons, chaos erupted all around the globe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You were sent as a last hope to find truth about the nature of the whale and hopefully lead the lost researchers back to the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
